txt.en: '[placeholder], I must tell you of a powerful morroval the Rangers encountered. They tell me they heard beautiful singing while scouting, and when they went to investigate the source, the Blood-singer fell on them with thrashing claws and terrible magic. Not all of them made it back alive. We must defeat this monster before more lives are lost!'
Dolenthol is stationed inside Barad Elenath, the Star-gazers' Spire.\n\nYou should talk to Dolenthol.
'She is defeated? Thank you, [placeholder]. The Rangers will be pleased to hear their fallen comrades have been avenged.'
The Rangers have identified a powerful morroval in the Circle of Madness. You are tasked with defeating him.
Blood-singer Maurgol can be found somewhere in the Circle of Madness.\n\nDefeat Blood-singer Maurgol.
